albinism believed to strengthen the power of the king in the Dogon cosmology and in the Bambara 
Kingdom. Aleksandra Cimpric, <i>Children Accused of Witchcraft: An anthropological study of 
contemporary practices in Africa</i> (Dakar, UNICEF, 2010), p. 28. Available from 
www.unicef.org/wcaro/wcaro_children-accused-of-witchcraft-in-Africa.pdf.  
</p>
